{"tid":1777054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港人屌台灣人血饅頭，其實同海底奇兵屌人唔落黎救佢一鳩樣。","createTime":"2019-12-10T03:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T04:48:12.000Z","uid":33904,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aff1c01109ec6b886783bdc4136ae57c29465aad","tid":1777054,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"「人國兩制就係海底奇兵」<br />\n<br />\n自己on9行錯路仆左街，<br />\n人地見到條路有伏唔踩落去就話人：人血饅頭。<br />\n仲要大叫：「屌你老味！ 快d落黎救我！」<br />\n<br />\n人地幫你拎住d野已經算好人，<br />\n仲叫人快d落水幫拖？<br />\n正常人都會覆你：「下？點落啊？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZVidzTIHYsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZVidzTIHYsM&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=2a907c25\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZVidzTIHYsM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一：台灣到而家有冇迫香港義士走？<br />\n<br />\n第二：蔡英文贏左未？<br />\n<br />\n未贏既，點解要迫佢呢一刻高調做d減低佢勝算既野？人地話有份寫港澳條例，寫既時候預埋呢個情況，你咪等人贏左睇下點，<br />\n係都要逼人搞難民法，又冇人趕義士走。<br />\n比韓國魚贏鳩左，全部義士送哂中就開心啦，比少少政治智慧啦屌！"},{"pid":"c6e8535ee7a5c8a0a2b35b4388469172bc0ade9a","tid":1777054,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"近排Ptt好多分化港台既Post"},{"pid":"822d89ff5ecd418de4df77c17b03e2abc5f59740","tid":1777054,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"堅持攬抄<br />\n商家唔洗諗有返生意<br />\n簡單和你shop,和你唱 ,和你lunch已經好有用<br />\n唔好諗住聖誕,新年,復活有生意做<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\nFB page: 二百萬三罷聯合陣線<br />\nTG頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=9f29bbfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nGroup List <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F186&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=b0e296bd\" data-aut